What was missing from the emotional support you got at that time — from health professionals, your partner, or people around you? 

If it helps to think about it, you can say:
- Something a midwife, nurse, or doctor could have said or done that would have helped;
- Something you wished your partner had said or done;
- Or something your friends, family, or neighbours could have done.

Can you give one or two specific examples or a moment when you felt especially alone or unsupported?
